--[[ The onLoad event is called after the game save finishes loading. --]]
function onLoad()
    universalDeck = getObjectFromGUID("34acdf")
    resourceDeck = getObjectFromGUID("8d7b7f")
    cubeBag = getObjectFromGUID("19d8a1")
    roomDeck = getObjectFromGUID("35b5e9")
    easyChecker = getObjectFromGUID("3f6819")
    mediumChecker = getObjectFromGUID("cea98c")
    hardChecker = getObjectFromGUID("5b6ca7")
    veteranChecker = getObjectFromGUID("eef526")
    lockZone = getObjectFromGUID("e36d75")
    trashBag = getObjectFromGUID("e6a164")
    damageOne = getObjectFromGUID("4cb068")
    damageTwo = getObjectFromGUID("100777")
    damageThree = getObjectFromGUID("df1a02")
    whitePawn = getObjectFromGUID("a9d1fa")
    bluePawn = getObjectFromGUID("a99fa3")
    redPawn = getObjectFromGUID("438712")
    yellowPawn = getObjectFromGUID("d16858")
    blueReference = getObjectFromGUID("db46cd")
    whiteReference = getObjectFromGUID("9b683e")
    yellowReference = getObjectFromGUID("9ec3d3")
    redReference = getObjectFromGUID("a1ac2e")

    easyChecker.createButton(easyButton)
    mediumChecker.createButton(mediumButton)
    hardChecker.createButton(hardButton)
    veteranChecker.createButton(veteranButton)
end

function setupEasy()
    easyGame = true
    setupGame()
    easyChecker.removeButton(0)
    mediumChecker.removeButton(0)
    hardChecker.removeButton(0)
    veteranChecker.removeButton(0)
end

function setupMedium()
    mediumGame = true
    setupGame()
    easyChecker.removeButton(0)
    mediumChecker.removeButton(0)
    hardChecker.removeButton(0)
    veteranChecker.removeButton(0)
end

function setupHard()
    hardGame = true
    setupGame()
    easyChecker.removeButton(0)
    mediumChecker.removeButton(0)
    hardChecker.removeButton(0)
    veteranChecker.removeButton(0)
end

function setupVeteran()
    veteranGame = true
    setupGame()
    easyChecker.removeButton(0)
    mediumChecker.removeButton(0)
    hardChecker.removeButton(0)
    veteranChecker.removeButton(0)
end

function setupGame()
    playerCheck()
    setDifficulty()
    shuffleRooms()
    setupTimer("placeRooms", 1)
    setupTimer("placeCubes", 3)
    setupTimer("shuffleResources", 3)
    setupTimer("dealCards", 4)
    setupTimer("drawPile", 5)
    setupTimer("eventDeck", 5)
    setupTimer("placePawns", 6)
    setupTimer("cleanUp", 6)
    setupTimer("firstPlayer", 7)
end

function playerCheck()
    if Player.White.seated == true then
        whiteSeated = true
        playerCount = playerCount + 1
    end
    if Player.Blue.seated == true then
        blueSeated = true
        playerCount = playerCount + 1
    end
    if Player.Red.seated == true then
        redSeated = true
        playerCount = playerCount + 1
    end
    if Player.Yellow.seated == true then
        yellowSeated = true
        playerCount = playerCount + 1
    end
end

function setDifficulty()
    if easyGame == true then
        resourceDeck.putObject(universalDeck)
    end
    if mediumGame == true then
        for i = 1, 4, 1 do
            resourceDeck.putObject(universalDeck.takeObject({index = 0}))
        end
        trashBag.putObject(universalDeck)
    end
    if hardGame == true then
        for i = 1, 2, 1 do
            resourceDeck.putObject(universalDeck.takeObject({index = 0}))
        end
        trashBag.putObject(universalDeck)
    end
    if veteranGame == true then
        trashBag.putObject(universalDeck)
    end
end

function shuffleRooms()
    roomDeck.shuffle()
end

function placeRooms()
    for i = 1, 8, 1 do
        location = roomPositions[i]
        roomDeck.takeObject({index = 0, position = location, rotation = {0.00, 180, 0.00}})
    end
    setupTimer("lockRooms", 1)
end

function lockRooms()
    for i, obj in ipairs(lockZone.getObjects()) do
        obj.setLock(true)
    end
end

function placeCubes()
    for i = 1, 24, 1 do
        location = cubePositions[i]
        cubeBag.takeObject({index = 0, position = location})
    end
end

function shuffleResources()
    resourceDeck.shuffle()
end

function dealCards()
    if playerCount == 1 then
        resourceDeck.deal(4)
    end
    if playerCount == 2 then
        resourceDeck.deal(4)
    end
    if playerCount == 3 then
        resourceDeck.deal(3)
    end
    if playerCount == 4 then
        resourceDeck.deal(2)
    end
end

function drawPile()
    for i = 1, 2, 1 do
        location = drawCardPositions[i]
        resourceDeck.takeObject({index = 0, position = location, rotation = drawCardRotation})
    end
end

function eventDeck()
    damageOne.shuffle()
    damageTwo.shuffle()
    damageThree.shuffle()
    for i = 1, 2, 1 do
        location = damagePositions[i]
        damageThree.takeObject({index = 0, position = location, rotation = {0, 180, 0}})
    end
    damageThree.setPositionSmooth(eventPosition)
    setupTimer("moveTwos", 1)
    setupTimer("moveOnes", 2)
end

function moveTwos()
    damageTwo.setPositionSmooth(eventPosition)
end

function moveOnes()
    damageOne.setPositionSmooth(eventPosition)
end

function placePawns()
    if playerCount == 1 then
        whiteReference.setPositionSmooth(soloReferenceCards[1])
        whiteReference.setRotation({0, 180, 0})
        blueReference.setPositionSmooth(soloReferenceCards[2])
        blueReference.setRotation({0, 180, 0})
        yellowReference.setPositionSmooth(soloReferenceCards[3])
        yellowReference.setRotation({0, 180, 0})
        whitePawn.setPositionSmooth(whitePosition)
        bluePawn.setPositionSmooth(bluePosition)
        yellowPawn.setPositionSmooth(yellowPosition)
        redPawn.setPositionSmooth(extraPawn)
    end
    if whiteSeated == true then
        whitePawn.setPositionSmooth(whitePosition)
    end
    if blueSeated == true then
        bluePawn.setPositionSmooth(bluePosition)
    end
    if redSeated == true then
        redPawn.setPositionSmooth(redPosition)
    end
    if yellowSeated == true then
        yellowPawn.setPositionSmooth(yellowPosition)
    end
end

function cleanUp()
    if playerCount > 1 then
        if whiteSeated == false then
            trashBag.putObject(whitePawn)
        end
        if blueSeated == false then
            trashBag.putObject(bluePawn)
        end
        if redSeated == false then
            trashBag.putObject(redPawn)
        end
        if yellowSeated == false then
            trashBag.putObject(yellowPawn)
        end
    else
        trashBag.putObject(redReference)
    end
end

function firstPlayer()
    playerPicked = false
    while playerPicked == false do
        num = math.random(1,4)
        if num == 1 and whiteSeated == true then
            broadcastToAll("White was randomly chosen to go first", {r=1, g=1, b=1})
            playerPicked = true
            Turns.turn_color = "White"
        end
        if num == 2 and blueSeated == true then
            broadcastToAll("Blue was randomly chosen to go first", {r=0, g=0, b=1})
            playerPicked = true
            Turns.turn_color = "Blue"
        end
        if num == 3 and redSeated == true then
            broadcastToAll("Red was randomly chosen to go first", {r=1, g=0, b=0})
            playerPicked = true
            Turns.turn_color = "Red"
        end
        if num == 4 and yellowSeated == true then
            broadcastToAll("Yellow was randomly chosen to go first", {r=1, g=1, b=0})
            playerPicked = true
            Turns.turn_color = "Yellow"
        end
    end
end

function setupTimer(fcnName, delay) --timer for executing functions in the correct order
    Timer.create({
        identifier = tostring({}), -- unique name
        function_name = fcnName,    -- what it triggers
        function_owner = self,
        delay = delay,              -- delay in seconds
        repetitions = 1,            -- oneshot
    })
end
